# --- Open-core boundary: skills (MUST mirror .dockerignore) ---------------------
# DEFAULT-DENY so `git add -A` can never stage a company/overlay skill (e.g.
# skills/snowflake with internal schema + ARR figures) into the public repo.
# Only the generic CORE skills below are tracked; everything else stays local.
# Keep this list in sync with the !skills/... allowlist in .dockerignore.
skills/*
!skills/anti-slop/
!skills/api-conventions/
!skills/autoplan/
!skills/brainstorm/
!skills/capability-routing/
!skills/challenge/
