# --- Private overlay (see docs/OVERLAY.md) ------------------------------------
# Host-side plugins: any services/host/overlay_*.go self-registers into
# pi-stack-host via init() when present, and is kept out of git. The public binary
# builds and runs identically without them.
services/host/overlay_*.go
# The private mixin kit — company skills, full capabilities.json, the snow wrapper,
# and overlay make targets — lives here, entirely gitignored.
pi-kit-work/
